      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="15701794">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/taishizheng/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1472187-44.jpg" alt="太史政" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15701794/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15701794/" class="">第181页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/taishizheng/" class=" " title="太史政">太史政</a>
                (下舍风萧条，寒草满户庭)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15701794">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">盧逮會《五代十國對遼的外交》
當為盧逮曾，蓋『曾』字頭上兩點寫得像『八』時，會被誤認為『會』字。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15701794/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-12-07 00:08</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>盧逮會《五代十國對遼的外交》</q></blockquote>
當為盧逮曾，蓋『曾』字頭上兩點寫得像『八』時，會被誤認為『會』字。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

